urring|Recurring}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Mark Elderkin\n| Pastor Lambrick\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n| Neels Clasen\n| Hamund\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| [[Langley Kirkwood]]\n| Captain Dyfed Bryson\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Andre Jacobs\n| De Groot\n| colspan=\"4\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n|-\n| Dean McCoubrey\n| Hayes\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Garth Collins\n| Albinus\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| [[Karl Otto Thaning|Karl Thaning]]\n| O'Malley\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Richard Wright-Firth\n| Muldoon\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n| John Herbert\n| Captain Geoffrey Lawrence\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| David Dukas\n| Captain Hume\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| [[Sibongile Mlambo]]\n| Eme\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n| Patrick Lavisa\n| Babatunde\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Tadhg Murphy\n| [[Edward Low|Ned Low]]\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Nic Rasenti\n| Mr. Holmes\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Robert Hobbs\n| Jenks\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Meganne Young\n| Abigail Ashe\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Laudo Liebenberg\n| Dooley\n| {{CNone}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n|-\n| Adrian Collins\n| Vincent\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n| Tyrel Meyer\n| Nicholas\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-