om/2018/03/13/opinions/tillerson-firing-makes-head-explode-opinion-miller/index.html|title=Longtime diplomat: Tillerson's public firing makes my head explode|last=Miller|first=Aaron David|publisher=CNN|access-date=March 13, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180313174240/https://www.cnn.com/2018/03/13/opinions/tillerson-firing-makes-head-explode-opinion-miller/index.html|archive-date=March 13, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[File:Thomas A. Shannon Jr official photo (cropped).jpg|100px]]<br>[[Thomas A. Shannon Jr.]]\n| style=\"background:gold\" | January 20, 2017 \n| style=\"background:gold\" | February 1, 2017\n|\n|-\n| [[File:US_Department_of_State_official_seal.svg|70x70px]]<br>[[Under Secretary of State for Political Affairs|Under Secretary of State (Political Affairs)]]\n| February 12, 2016 \n| June 4, 2018\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[File:US_Department_of_State_official_seal.svg|70x70px]]<br>[[United States Deputy Secretary of State|Deputy Secretary of State]]\n| style=\"background:gold\" | February 1, 2017 \n| style=\"background:gold\" | May 24, 2017\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[File:John J Sullivan.jpg|100px]]<br>[[John J. Sullivan (diplomat)|John Sullivan]]\n| May 24, 2017 \n| December 20, 2019\n| Became Ambassador to Russia\n|-\n| [[File:Seal_of_the_United_States_Secretary_of_State.svg|70x70px]]<br>[[United States Secretary of State|Secretary of State]]\n| style=\"background:gold\" | March 31, 2018 \n| style=\"background:gold\" | April 26, 2018\n| \n|-\n| [[File:M peterlinaa.jpg|100px]]<br>[[Margaret Peterlin]]\n| [[File:US_Department_of_State_official_seal.svg|70x70px]]<br>[[Chief of Staff to the United States Secretary of State|Chief of Staff to the Secretary of State]]\n| February 12, 2017\n| March 31, 2018\n|\n|-\n| [[File:P. Michael McKinley official photo.jpg|100px]]<br>[[P. Michael McKinley|Michael McKinley]]\n| [[File:US_Department_of_State_official_seal.svg|70x70px]]<br>Senior Advisor to the Secretary of State\n| No