/quantitativepeace.com/blog/2017/02/on-michael-flynns-tenure-as-national-security-advisor.html|archive-date=February 15, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"HawkinsShortest\">Derek Hawkins, [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/02/14/flynn-sets-record-with-only-24-days-as-nsc-chief-the-average-tenure-is-about-2-6-years/ Flynn sets record with only 24 days as national security advisor. The average tenure is about 2.6 years.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411150059/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/02/14/flynn-sets-record-with-only-24-days-as-nsc-chief-the-average-tenure-is-about-2-6-years/ |date=April 11, 2019 }}, ''Washington Post'' (February 14, 2017).</ref>\n|-\n| [[File:H.R. McMaster ARCIC 2014.jpg|100px]]<br>[[H. R. McMaster]]\n| February 20, 2017\n| April 9, 2018\n| McMaster was criticized in August 2017 after he fired several [[United States National Security Council|National Security Council]] staff members,<ref>{{Citation|title=Smear campaign targets McMaster \u2013 CNN Video|url=http://edition.cnn.com/videos/politics/2017/08/04/mcmaster-smear-campaign-steve-bannon-starr-lead-dnt.cnn|access-date=August 22, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822095011/http://edition.cnn.com/videos/politics/2017/08/04/mcmaster-smear-campaign-steve-bannon-starr-lead-dnt.cnn|archive-date=August 22, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/congress/sen-mccain-decries-criticism-of-mcmaster-as-smear-tactics/2017/08/14/08772d5e-8135-11e7-9e7a-20fa8d7a0db6_story.html|title=Sen. McCain decries criticism of McMaster as 'smear tactics'|website=Washington Post|access-date=August 22, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822101138/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/congress/sen-mccain-decries-criticism-of-mcmaster-as-smear-tactics/2017/08/14/08772d5e-8135-11e7-9e7a-20fa8d7a0db6_story.html|archive-date=August 22, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{